title: Behind the Lens: Summer 2013 Volcom Apparel
description: Take a look behind the camera lens with this candid apparel video shoot. Model and Volcomunity ambassador Stephanie Cherry shows us her style in front of the camera as well as the new Summer 2013 Volcom apparel collection.
